        "end": 11
      },
      {
        "text": "丞相",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 103,
        "end": 105
      },
      {
        "text": "幸得賜餐錢奉邑",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 140,
        "end": 147
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_003_000017",
    "sentence": "春正月乙卯，地震，羌道、武都道山崩。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_003_000018",
    "sentence": "夏六月丙 戌晦，日有蝕之。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_003_000019",
    "sentence": "秋七月，恆山王不疑薨。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_003_000020",
    "sentence": "行八銖錢。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_006_003_000021",
    "sentence": "三年",
    "entities": [
